flowchart TB
  %% Diagram 75A: Partner API Trust and Access Business-Friendly Map

  Request[Partner requests API access]
  Approve[Platform approves allowed permissions]
  Key[Secure API key issued and protected]
  Use[Partner uses API for approved operations]
  Check[System checks scope and rate limits on every call]

  Good{Request compliant?}
  Allow[Request succeeds]
  Deny[Request blocked safely]
  Rotate[Keys are rotated regularly]
  Revoke[Compromised keys are revoked immediately]

  Request --> Approve --> Key --> Use --> Check --> Good
  Good -- Yes --> Allow --> Rotate --> Use
  Good -- No --> Deny --> Revoke
